{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Astarion is resting in his bedroll when he has a nightmare about Cazador carving the scars into his back."
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "9": {
      "id": "9",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*You rarely rest well, but tonight something feels different. Whether it's the parasite within your brain or the darkness without, you're deeply uneasy.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "3": {
          "id": "3",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*Again and again, your thoughts return to memories of pain. Of suffering. Of Cazador.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "23": {
              "id": "23",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*You remember his small cruelties. You remember his sadistic whims. And you remember the long night he spent carving 'poetry' into your back.*",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "21": {
                  "id": "21",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*Deep in your trance it all feels vividly real again - the jagged cuts of the 'needle' he used on you, the shapes he traced into your flesh. You can almost tell what he's writing.*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "18": {
                      "id": "18",
                      "speaker": "Astarion",
                      "text": "Focus on the pain in your back - try to understand what he's carving.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "15": {
                          "id": "15",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Your body is racked by agony, but you push through it, carefully tracking the movement and position of every tear and slice.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "rollresult",
                          "children": {
                            "4": {
                              "id": "4",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*Your body is racked by agony, but you push through it, carefully tracking the movement and position of every tear and slice.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "13": {
                                  "id": "13",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*Despite the horror your body feels, you slowly start to build up a picture of what your old master carved, recognising not words, but runes. Infernal runes.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "20": {
                                      "id": "20",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*Unable to decipher the arcane symbols, you have to admit defeat and give yourself over to the pain.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "17": {
                                          "id": "17",
                                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                                          "text": "*You spend the rest of the night reliving your torment, but if nothing else, you know your scars are not what they seemed to be.*",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "16": {
                          "id": "16",
                          "speaker": "",
                          "text": "*You try to focus, but the pain is too much. As one cut flows into the next you lose all track of their shapes, leaving you with nothing but a haze of pain.*",
                          "context": "",
